    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte individuaeque trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/172">Ardoinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> divina providente clemencia secundum
                        volumtatem dei salvatoris nostrique liberatoris. Quicquid confirmacionis et
                        proprietatis ad aecclesiarum dei sanctorumque suorum exaltacionem
                        prebuerimus, id nobis ad aeterne beatitudinis bravium et secularis vite
                        profectum esse profuturum verissime credimus. Igitur omnium sanctae dei
                        aecclesiae fidelium nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum agnoscat
                        universitas, qualiter nos pro dei omnipotentis amore et ob remedium animae
                        nostre parentumque nostrorum, rogante domno <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbate</rs>, suo <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs> ad honorem
                        <orgName
                            key="#Rivers #Mountains #Villas #Curtes #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Saltworks #Mills #Penalty #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Castle #Ports #Other_administrative_unit #Assembly #Angaria #Tolls #Teloneum #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity #Churches #Monasteries #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3619">sancti
                            Salvatoris</orgName> haud procul a menibus <placeName key="#Palatium" ref="#places/65"
                            >Ticinensis</placeName> urbis fundato per hoc nostrum regale preceptum,
                        prout iuste et legaliter valemus, confirmamus, quemadmodum a <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/7">tertius Otto</persName> preceptali
                        auctoritate confirmata sunt, omnia, que eidem venerabili loco donata collata
                        et oblata sunt, tam de largifluo dono bone memoriae domne <persName
                            key="#Queen" ref="#people/1301">Adadheleide</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatrice</rs> quam eciam aliqua inscriptione cartarum
                        aliorum hominum, cum <rs key="#Castle">castellis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Villas">villis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Curtes">cortibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">capellis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">oratoriis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs> vallibus planiciebus <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> cultis et incultis <rs
                            key="#Tolls #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ripis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Ports">portibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">ancillis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldionibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldianis</rs>, verum eciam cum omnibus, de quibus
                        venerabile coenobium iuste investituram habet vel habuit ex ea die, qua
                        serenissima quondam memorata Adhaelegida <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> ibi
                        constituit. Confirmamus quidem et firmissima tradicione largimur eidem
                        monasterio sancti Salvatoris <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            >sancti Anastasii</orgName> cum omni sua pertinentia una cum <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Curtes 
                            #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/342">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Curtes 
                                #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/134">Olonna</geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Montecelli</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Erbariam</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Basiliuciam</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Frixinariam</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Riuum
                            ceruinum</placeName>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> de
                            <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Petrus Albesanus">Petro
                                Albesano </name></persName>, terram quam tenuit <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Liudualdus"
                            >Liutaldus</name></persName> cum <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs> de
                            <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">
                            Pelenzuna</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Tollianum</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Pastorianum</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Cauconate</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Uergemini</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Garlascum</placeName> cum <rs key="#Other_administrative_unit"
                            >districtu</rs> duum miliarum per in circuitu, <rs>viridiarium</rs>
                        prope Palatinam portam et sancti Iohannis situm cum omnibus pertinentiis
                        suis et adiacentiis tam infra civitatem Ticinensem quam extra, Pratum
                        regium. Insuper <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Saltworks #Oil #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">sancte dei genitricis Mariae</orgName> in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pomposa</placeName> dicto constructum et
                        omnia, que in <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/485"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/2449"> Comaglo</geogName></placeName> eidem monasterio
                        pertinent infra <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs> seu extra, tam in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Reda</placeName>
                        quam in <placeName key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4882">Quinto</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/3520">Corua ceruina</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches" ref="#places/77"
                            >Figariolo</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4883">Zunzadega</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4884">Zunziano</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4885">Sareniano</placeName> et omnes <rs key="#Saltworks"
                            >salinas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Oil">olivaeta</rs> vel omnia que ad iam dictum monasterium sancte
                        dei genitricis Mariae vel ad alia loca omnia, que coenobio sancti salvatoris
                        domini nostri Iesu Christi pertinere videntur, tam ibi quam in caeteris
                        aliis locis, nec non <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Armentaria</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Blundi</placeName> cum pertinentiis ineffabilibus illo in proprium
                        corroboravimus. Precipientes itaque iubemus, ut nullus <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Immunity">nullaque regni nostri magna parvaque persona de rebus
                            mobilibus sive inmobilibus sive de qualibet terra disvestire idem
                            monasterium sine legali iudicio presumat</rs>. Sancimus insuper et hac
                        nostra regali auctoritate concedimus, ut, si contigerit, quod sepe accidit,
                        quatinus <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> prenominati monasterii huius lucis
                        habitaculum deserat, liceat monachos ex sinu eiusdem ecclesiae quem meliorem
                        viderint eligere in patrem, omnium episcoporum vel omnium mortalium
                        contradictione remota, nec fas sit alicui monacho ex alio monasterio ad id
                        transitum facere sine voluntate monachorum inibi deo servientium
                        imperpetuum. Si quis autem huius nostrae promulgate auctorit[atis] et
                        precepti violator extiterit sive predicte ecclesiae sancti Salvatoris
                        minoracionem facere aut in castellis villis vel aliquibuslibet locis eius
                        aribergare, <rs key="#Assembly">placitum</rs> sine eiusdem [c]enobii abbatis iussione ullatenus
                        tenere aut aliquam <rs key="#Angaria">angariam</rs> puplicam functionem aut 
                        <rs key="#Teloneum">theloneum</rs> extorquere aut
                        tollere vel monachos de aliqua re presumpserit molestare, sciat se
                        compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri cocti libras mille</rs>, medietatem 
                        <rs key="#Camera_regis">kamere nostre</rs> ac
                        medietatem <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">abbati eiusdem monasterii</rs>, 
                        qui pro tempore fuerit, et insuper,
                        quod ei deterius est, cum Iuda traditore domini salvatoris nostri, in cuius
                        nomine iam dictum monasterium constructum est, aeternis deputetur incendiis.
                        Ut autem verius credatur hoc preceptum nostrae auctoritate peractum,
                        presentem paginam manu propria, ut videtur infra, corroborantes sigillo
                        nostro iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Ardoini (M.) regis invictissimi.
                        <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Cunibertus">Cunibertus</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice 
                        <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> Cumani <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> 
                            <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs>
                        regognovit. (SI. D). Data X. kal. mra. mar. anno dominicae incarnacionis
                        MII, indictione XV, anno domni Ardoini regis regnante I; actum in Papiensi
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palacio</rs>; feliciter amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
